{"image_id": "CINF_2013_page_68", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "Cincinnati Financial Corporation - 2013 10-K - Page 66", "bbox": [435.0, 1566.8, 839.8, 1585.4]}, {"text": "(Dollars in millions)", "bbox": [110.4, 96.1, 246.5, 114.5]}, {"text": "Accident year loss and loss expenses incurred and ratios to earned premiums:", "bbox": [110.4, 120.9, 755.5, 143.9]}, {"text": "Accident Year:", "bbox": [122.9, 150.0, 249.6, 173.1]}, {"text": "2013", "bbox": [584.4, 150.0, 626.0, 173.1]}, {"text": "2012", "bbox": [686.5, 150.0, 728.1, 173.1]}, {"text": "2011", "bbox": [788.9, 150.0, 830.5, 173.1]}, {"text": "2013", "bbox": [890.6, 150.0, 932.3, 173.1]}, {"text": "2012", "bbox": [992.7, 150.0, 1034.4, 173.1]}, {"text": "2011", "bbox": [1095.1, 150.0, 1136.8, 173.1]}, {"text": "as of December 31, 2013", "bbox": [135.4, 179.2, 344.3, 202.3]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [564.6, 179.0, 575.0, 202.0]}, {"text": "1,691", "bbox": [598.2, 179.0, 645.1, 202.0]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [666.7, 179.0, 677.1, 202.0]}, {"text": "1,646", "bbox": [700.3, 179.0, 747.2, 202.0]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [768.8, 179.0, 779.2, 202.0]}, {"text": "1,685", "bbox": [802.4, 179.0, 849.3, 202.0]}, {"text": "64.1%", "bbox": [901.0, 179.0, 958.3, 202.0]}, {"text": "69.1%", "bbox": [1003.1, 179.0, 1060.4, 202.0]}, {"text": "76.7%", "bbox": [1105.2, 179.0, 1162.5, 202.0]}, {"text": "as of December 31, 2012", "bbox": [135.4, 208.4, 344.3, 231.4]}, {"text": "1,712", "bbox": [700.3, 208.4, 747.2, 231.4]}, {"text": "1,711", "bbox": [802.4, 208.4, 849.3, 231.4]}, {"text": "71.8", "bbox": [1003.1, 208.4, 1039.6, 231.4]}, {"text": "77.9", "bbox": [1105.2, 208.4, 1141.7, 231.4]}, {"text": "as of December 31, 2011", "bbox": [135.4, 237.5, 344.3, 260.6]}, {"text": "1,804", "bbox": [802.4, 237.5, 849.3, 260.6]}, {"text": "82.1", "bbox": [1105.2, 237.5, 1141.7, 260.6]}, {"text": "Catastrophe losses, as discussed in Consolidated Property Casualty Insurance Results of Operations, explain", "bbox": [104.2, 310.3, 1122.0, 333.6]}, {"text": "much of the movement in current accident year loss and loss expense ratios for accident years 2011 through 2013.", "bbox": [104.2, 335.3, 1166.9, 358.6]}, {"text": "Catastrophe losses added 4.3 percentage points for 2013, 8.9 points for 2012 and 10.3 points for 2011 to the", "bbox": [104.2, 360.3, 1111.4, 383.6]}, {"text": "respective commercial lines current accident year loss and loss expense ratios in the table above.", "bbox": [104.2, 385.3, 1003.8, 408.6]}, {"text": "The 59.8 percent ratio for current accident year loss and loss expenses before catastrophe losses for", "bbox": [104.2, 435.3, 1039.8, 458.6]}, {"text": "2013 improved 3.1 percentage points compared with the 62.9 percent accident year 2012 ratio measured as of", "bbox": [104.2, 460.3, 1129.0, 483.6]}, {"text": "December 31, 2012. Large losses, described below, and the corresponding ratios for new losses above", "bbox": [104.2, 485.3, 1060.7, 508.6]}, {"text": "$250,000 contributed a 0.3 percentage-point increase to the 2013 ratio. We believe the overall ratio reduction was", "bbox": [104.2, 510.3, 1157.6, 533.6]}, {"text": "largely due to higher pricing and initiatives to improve pricing precision and loss experience related to claims and", "bbox": [104.2, 535.3, 1146.2, 558.6]}, {"text": "loss control practices, somewhat offset by normal loss cost inflation.", "bbox": [104.2, 560.3, 729.0, 583.6]}, {"text": "Commercial lines reserve development on prior accident years continued to net to a favorable amount in 2013, as", "bbox": [104.2, 610.3, 1155.6, 633.6]}, {"text": "$95 million was recognized, a lower benefit than the $292 million recognized in 2012. Of the $197 million decrease", "bbox": [104.2, 635.3, 1163.7, 658.6]}, {"text": "in 2013 compared with 2012, $144 million was attributable to re-estimates of IBNR. More than 85 percent of our", "bbox": [104.2, 660.3, 1137.0, 683.6]}, {"text": "commercial lines reserve development on prior accident years recognized during 2013 occurred in our commercial", "bbox": [104.2, 685.3, 1162.4, 708.6]}, {"text": "casualty and workers’ compensation lines of business, with approximately 70 percent occurring in commercial", "bbox": [104.2, 710.3, 1118.8, 733.6]}, {"text": "casualty. Development recognized during 2012 and 2011 was also mostly from our commercial casualty and", "bbox": [104.2, 735.3, 1105.0, 758.6]}, {"text": "workers’ compensation lines of business. Development by line of business and other trends for commercial lines", "bbox": [104.2, 760.3, 1142.0, 783.6]}, {"text": "loss and loss expenses and the related ratios are further analyzed in Commercial Lines of Business Analysis and in", "bbox": [104.2, 785.3, 1170.7, 808.6]}, {"text": "Liquidity and Capital Resources, Consolidated Property Casualty Insurance Development of Estimated Reserves by", "bbox": [104.2, 810.3, 1176.4, 833.6]}, {"text": "Accident Year.", "bbox": [104.2, 835.3, 236.2, 858.6]}, {"text": "Commercial Lines Insurance Losses by Size", "bbox": [104.2, 885.3, 543.0, 908.6]}, {"text": "(Dollars in millions)", "bbox": [110.4, 931.5, 246.5, 950.0]}, {"text": "Years ended December 31,", "bbox": [647.6, 927.1, 873.2, 950.2]}, {"text": "2013-2012", "bbox": [929.8, 926.9, 1020.1, 950.0]}, {"text": "2012-2011", "bbox": [1051.0, 927.1, 1141.3, 950.2]}, {"text": "2013", "bbox": [636.5, 956.1, 678.1, 979.1]}, {"text": "2012", "bbox": [738.5, 956.3, 780.2, 979.4]}, {"text": "2011", "bbox": [840.9, 956.3, 882.6, 979.4]}, {"text": "Change %", "bbox": [927.8, 956.1, 1022.1, 979.1]}, {"text": "Change %", "bbox": [1052.7, 956.3, 1138.9, 979.4]}, {"text": "New losses greater than $4,000,000", "bbox": [110.4, 985.5, 407.8, 1008.5]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [616.7, 985.2, 627.1, 1008.3]}, {"text": "82", "bbox": [662.5, 985.2, 683.3, 1008.3]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [718.8, 985.5, 729.2, 1008.5]}, {"text": "68", "bbox": [768.0, 985.5, 788.9, 1008.5]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [820.8, 985.5, 831.3, 1008.5]}, {"text": "56", "bbox": [870.1, 985